Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:24.74,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{コーチ足るものはそんな無責任な。}A coach cannot be this irresponsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:26.46,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{お言葉を返すようですが。}I'd like you to take that back, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:30.40,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{私はバレー部のコーチに就任した時はっきり申し上げたはずです。}I believe I made myself clear when I asked to become the coach.
