Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.17,0:12:33.06,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,{ん、ん。}H-Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:36.17,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{私は…}I…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:37.69,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{…あの子達は好きなんです。}…love these girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:39.35,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{可愛いんです。}I hold them dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:40.66,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{だからこそ。}And that is why…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:42.66,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{私はこうするんです。}…I'm doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.82,0:13:06.42,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{いよいよこの時は来たわ。}Finally we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:08.42,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{後は体当たりでぶつかるまでよ。}Now is the time to go all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:13.98,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{どうしたの、皆？}What is it, girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:14.81,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{ファイトがないわよ。}Where's your spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:16.97,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,{だ-だってXXX大きいですもの。}B-But they're so tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.97,0:13:19.30,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,{相手XX高校生XX大学生見たいわ。}They have this varsity vibe around them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:20.39,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{何言ってるの？}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:21.63,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{今から負けちゃだめよ。}We can't lose now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:24.00,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あたしたちは日本一のチームなのよ。}We're the best team in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:27.66,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{そうよ。今までの日本チームとは違うところを見せてあげるのよ。}Yeah. We'll show everyone we're different from the other Japan teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:36.58,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{ソ連女子ジュニアバレーチームもXXXの日本女子高校チームをそうなめにして…}The Soviet junior team, having annihilated all higher education teams in Japan…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:41.34,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{…今日ここに初めて日本の中学とXXXことに成りました。}…today for the first time plays against a Japanese middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:46.25,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{中学と言っても、この富士見学園は今年の春の全国大会で優勝したチームであり…}That middle school, the Fujimi Academy, won this year's spring All-Japan volleyball tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:50.00,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{一本もXXX自身をもっているようであります。}Looks like both teams don't intend to take a single step back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:52.92,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{果たして、日本が勝つか？ソ連が勝つか？}Ladies and gentlemen, will it be Japan or the Soviet Union who wins?
