Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:13.33,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{よし、行くわよ。}All right, here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:17.24,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{まず初っ端から変化球サーブ見舞ってソ連の度肝を抜いてやるわ。}Let's start with the curve ball right off the bat. It'll crush their confidence.
