Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:52.24,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{負けるもんか。}We won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:54.80,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{いいぞ、あゆはら！その調子！}Good, Ayuhara! Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.42,0:14:57.44,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{よかった。}I'm glad.
