Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:12.56,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,{そうそう。第二セットはこっちのものよ。}Yeah, yeah. The second set is ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:16.05,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,{そうXXXさ、いくらXXX相手でも、少しXXXわよ。}Maybe then they will open their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:17.23,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{行けない。}Damn.
