Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:39.14,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{すばらしいサーブ。}Excellent serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:40.90,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{これこそ本当のドライブサーブだ。}This is what gives "drive serve" its name.
