Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:38.49,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{頑張れ！}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:39.80,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{頑張れ！}You can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:42.36,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{こうなるとは分かってるとは言えん。}I won't say I knew this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:44.44,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{これではXXX可愛いそうだ。}I feel sorry for the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.44,0:19:46.17,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{だが。だが！}However. However!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.17,0:19:48.44,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{これは一度は味XX知れん。}This is something they need to learn the hard way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:50.03,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{それにしても。}But still.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.03,0:19:51.83,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{鮎原。頑張るんだ。}Ayuhara. Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:53.22,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{早川、しっかりしろ。}Hayakawa, you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:19:56.18,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{後ワンポイントで日本がXXX負け。}One point until Japan needs to admit defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.18,0:19:58.92,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{勝利は全く絶望的になりました。}The match became completely one-sided.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:01.30,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{初めてこずえの試合を見に来たんだ。}It's the first time when I can watch Kozue's game.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:02.84,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{こんな結果になるとは。}Who'd think it'd end up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:04.46,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{もう見ていられませんわ。}I can't watch it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:05.94,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{行きましょう。}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.24,0:20:13.21,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,{あ、あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.87,0:20:21.74,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{ついにソ連のXXXの前に、日本代表富士見学園チームはXXXました。}Finally, Japan's representative, Fujimi Academy collapses before the Soviet Union's team.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:24.94,Default,Commentator,0,0,0,,{それにしても、強い、ソ連ジュニアチーム。}Soviet's junior team is stronger after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.36,0:20:31.72,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{とうとう負けてしまった。}We completely lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.47,0:20:36.78,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{XXXプレーやトリックプレーを出すことにできずに負けてしまった。}We lost without using half of our tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:38.06,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:40.63,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あ、これが夢であってくれたのに。}Ah, my dream is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:43.28,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{鮎原。}Ayuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:44.71,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{残酷のようだが…}I hate to say it, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.71,0:20:46.17,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{…僕はこの日は来るの…}…but I've been waiting for this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.17,0:20:47.92,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{…君のその姿を待っていたんだ。}For this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.16,0:20:57.49,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{キャプテン鮎原。}Captain Ayuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.66,0:20:59.16,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:04.46,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{あなたたちこの前の全国大会で見せてくれた実力…}The power your team has shown us in the All-Japan tournament…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:06.18,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{十分発揮しなかった。}…wasn't there today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:09.46,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{特にあなたそうでした。}Yours especially.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:26.06,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{鮎原。又きっときっと会いましょう。}Ayuhara, let's meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:26.86,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.46,0:21:34.58,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,{それでさようなら。}Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:36.02,Default (ru),Shellenina,0,0,0,,До свидания.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.16,0:21:43.32,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{シェレーニナは「又会おう」と言ってくれたけど。}Shellenina wants to play again in the future, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:44.56,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{だけど。}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.56,0:21:46.51,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{これは何もかもお終いだわ。}…no matter how you look at it, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.62,0:22:06.78,Alternative,(mixed),0,0,0,,{—何やってんだよ？大きいなXXX。\N—XXX。}– You said we'll win.\N– You call yourself captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.78,0:22:10.10,Alternative,(unknown),0,0,0,,{XXXあんなXXX。}You were so full of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.10,0:22:12.83,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{昨夜一晩中寝ないで考えたんです。}I was thinking about this all night long without sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.83,0:22:16.47,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{先生、あたし決心しました。}Professor, I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.47,0:22:18.77,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{バレー部を解散してください。}Please disband the volleyball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:19.48,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{何？}Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.48,0:22:20.71,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{もうだめです。}It's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.71,0:22:24.85,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{バレー部専用体育館でころか、バレーさえこれ以上続けられません。}Without the new gym, our club cannot go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.85,0:22:26.67,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{何もかも終わりです。}Everything is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.67,0:22:27.62,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{鮎原。}Ayuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.82,0:22:30.89,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{き-きみは未だ分からんのか？}Y-You still don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.72,0:22:36.21,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{そんな考えしかできんのなら、望みどおりバレーなんか止めてしまえ。}If that's all you're thinking, be\hmy guest and quit volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:40.78,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{だが君一人のためにバレー部はあるんじゃない。}But the club isn't for you only.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.78,0:22:42.78,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{止めるなら、君一人で止めろ。}If you quit, do it by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.02,0:22:45.42,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{いいな？}Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:46.64,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そうします。}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.64,0:22:51.52,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{少し頭を冷やして、何のためにバレーをやるのかよく考えてみろ。}Cool down for a bit and think why you were playing volleyball thus far.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.52,0:22:54.89,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{それが分かるまで二度とバレー部に戻ってくるなよ。}Do not come back until you figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.22,0:23:02.54,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{鮎原。}Ayuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.54,0:23:04.60,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{何時俺は分かってくれるんだ？}When will you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.60,0:23:05.40,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{何時？}When?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:06.18,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{何時？}When?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.27,0:23:10.86,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{これでさっぱりしたわ。}This felt refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.86,0:23:13.13,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あたしはこれで責任を取ったんだわ。}I assumed responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.13,0:23:15.35,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{それで責任を取ったつもり？}Who are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.35,0:23:17.71,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あなたはただ逃げたのよ。}You just ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:18.70,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{違うわ。}That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.70,0:23:20.91,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{キャプテンとして責任を取ったのよ。}I assumed my responsibility as the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.91,0:23:22.91,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{これでバレーとのいっさいお別れ。}With this, I bid my farewell to volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.91,0:23:24.14,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{ハハハハ。}Hahahaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.14,0:23:26.81,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{本気でバレーが止められると思ってるの？}Do you really think you can quit volleyball?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.54,0:23:29.83,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{止められるわ。}I can quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.83,0:23:31.94,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{何のためにバレーをやるのかですって？}"What are you playing volleyball for?"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.84,0:23:34.66,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そんなこともう関係ないわ。}That doesn't matter anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.66,0:23:35.85,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{知るもんですか。}Who cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.40,0:23:56.52,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{XXXにもソ連チームのコーチはこずえを訪れ…}The Soviet Team's coach unexpectedly approaches Kozue…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.52,0:24:00.42,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{…シェレーニナは待っていると言う千本松原へこずえを連れ出した。}…and sends her to the pine grove, where Shellenina is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.42,0:24:02.96,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{シェレーニナは厳しくこずえに迫った。}Shellenina speaks harshly to Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.96,0:24:05.57,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{機能の試合ぶりを許せないと言うのだ。}"I can't forgive you the yesterday's match."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.57,0:24:07.11,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{バレーボールはどんなものか？}"What is volleyball about?"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.11,0:24:09.79,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{日本での最後の試合を見せたいと言う…}—she proclaims and declares she wants to show their last game in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.79,0:24:13.70,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{…その試合とはなんと、高校男子チームXXX。}The opponent is a high school boys' team.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.70,0:24:16.56,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{さて、試合はシェレーニナはこずえに見せおとした。}Shellenina shows Kozue the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.56,0:24:19.29,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{恐るべきプレーに向かって進んでいった。}It unfolds to be a terrifying game.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.29,0:24:23.04,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{さ、来週のアタックナンバーワンをお楽しみに。}Please look forward to the next episode.
